      "side": 1,
      "message": "This means we wouldn\u0027t even support making a texture even like this:\n glTexImage2D(GL_TEXTURE_2D, 0, GL_RGB, w, h, 0, GL_RGB, GR_GL_UNSIGNED_SHORT_5_6_5, ptr)\n\nwhich does not seem correct.",
