      "writtenOn": "2021-02-13T03:22:20Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Thanks Brian for the clarification.\nIt seems that Skia thinks the internal sized format GL_RGB565 is implicitly supported from external \u003cformat -- GL_RGB\u003e and \u003ctype -- GL_UNSIGNED_SHORT_5_6_5\u003e, while the validating cmd decoder strictly believes it\u0027s not allowed.\nI think they both aren\u0027t wrong. Personally I prefer to relax the validating cmd decoder for this.",
